description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for band 5 Paediatric trained nurses to join our enthusiastic and friendly department and become part of our supportive family.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paediatric Nursing is varied and extremely rewarding. Working with us will provide both newly qualified and experienced nurses with a broad range of skills and experiences which will help in your career progression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer rotational roles between Ward 3 our acute children’s ward and our Paediatric Decision Unit, giving you a real taste of the patient pathway. We provide all new starters with a robust induction programme and we have Practice Development Nurses on hand providing 1 -1 teaching and support in identifying your professional development needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a Registered Children’s Nurse or a student soon to qualify with a positive attitude to ensuring children receive the best possible care, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full-time and Part-time posts available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anna Kerr: anna.kerr@nhs.net:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Annette Hedley :annette.hedley2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or Telephone: 01296 316416&lt;/p&gt;
